{
  "stem": "5613.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, we had six months that he was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a bad one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, not as bad as in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they killed a lot of people there in these camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my brother belonged to a musical society.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Queen Mother-- Queen Elizabeth of Belgium-- was the honorary president or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So somebody who knew him wrote to her and explained, maybe she could do something for him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And apparently, through her interference, he was released six months later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he came out and this was--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our group, [HEBREW], continued.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as we had to stay in the-- we were not supposed to-- I was not supposed to leave the town or even the home, we used to organize-- every meeting we had-- one a month at that time-- we used to go to a home-- all of us-- meet in the home, and stay the whole night, sleep on the floor.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the morning, 7 o'clock, we used to go home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well-behaved-- everybody was well-behaved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this went on till the-- till the week before I was arrested, till 1942, April the 29th '42.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did some business in the bicycle accessory business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to-- I had old customers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to go to them, see them, and call them up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everything was black market, by the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing was kosher at that time anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever we did, was black market.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He used to go in to business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But every day or every other day, somebody was arrested there for one reason or another.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the diamond bourse-- he used to go to the diamond bourse every where-- every day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Germans used to come in, arrest a man, take him along.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, they had to pay a sum.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
